<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>Unless 'strict' is set to true, the validator just pass the test no matter which data is posted.</p>

<p><em>Works</em></p>

<pre class="highlight"><code>
$this-&gt;add($factory-&gt;createInput(array(
    'name'       =&gt; 'activity_type',
    'required'   =&gt; true,
    'validators' =&gt; array(
        array(
            'name' =&gt; 'InArray',
            'options' =&gt; array(
                'haystack' =&gt; array('test', 0, 'A'),
                'strict'   =&gt; true,
            ),
        ),
    ),
)));
</code></pre>

<p><em>Dont works</em></p>

<pre class="highlight"><code>
$this-&gt;add($factory-&gt;createInput(array(
    'name'       =&gt; 'activity_type',
    'required'   =&gt; true,
    'validators' =&gt; array(
        array(
            'name' =&gt; 'InArray',
            'options' =&gt; array(
                'haystack' =&gt; array('test', 0, 'A'),
            ),
        ),
    ),
)));
</code></pre>

